$$
\Delta\% = 100\% \cdot \frac{\widehat\beta_{FLR, full} - \widehat\beta_{FLR, red}}{\widehat\beta_{FLR, full}} = 100\% \cdot \frac{0.002 - 0.0036}{0.002} = -74.41\%
$$

-   Based off the percent change, I would keep this in the model

